INSERT INTO `project-information` VALUES (1,108,'2019/08','2020/07','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','子計畫:即時偵察與持續追蹤社群媒體中之災難事件情資(II)',NULL,NULL,'本計畫所研發的災難偵測與監控系統可廣泛應用於各類型災難事件，其早期告警機制讓政府及相關救災單位可快速啟動救援相關機制，並適當地調配相關救難人力資源。另與過往類似的學術研究工作非常不同，本計畫是與正式的災難應變機關合作，進行創新技術之開發並結合了跨領域的知能，預期能激起更多的延伸應用發展。',NULL),(2,108,'2019/06','2020/05','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','用於物流業之室內定位技術與倉儲管理系統',NULL,NULL,'對於物流業而言，本計畫所提室內即時定位系統與倉儲管理系統之整合應用，藉由適當的通訊技術來實現其對於大範圍與高精確度的要求，可減少人力成本、提升倉儲管理作業之效率與效益。同時，即時定位的追蹤與數據記錄，亦可成為發展智慧倉儲中自動化管理的基礎，未來結合穿戴式裝置與無人車等技術，可望進一步帶動相關產業升級。',NULL),(3,107,'2018/08','2019/07','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','子計畫:即時偵察與持續追蹤社群媒體中之災難事件情資(I)','資料分析、災難管理、緊急災難應變中心、社群媒體','data analytics, disaster management, emergency operation center, social media','自然或人為災難皆可能導致嚴重的人員傷亡和經濟損失，因此對相關機構而言最具挑戰性的任務之一，就是迅速且準確地掌握災難事件的最新狀況。而隨著近年來社群媒體 (如Twitter、Facebook、PTT等) 的普及，使得災難現場目擊的民眾可以藉由社群媒體發送即時訊息，以迅速聯繫親朋好友並分享相關資訊與照片、影音等，此一資訊傳播方式往往比傳統媒體中的新聞報導更加快速，而成為新型態的資訊管道。在本計畫中，我們認為災難管理之議題在不同時期可分為：災難發生時的應對、災難發生後的復原、平時 (災前) 的防患等三項重要任務，這也分別對應到本計畫執行期間的各年年度目標。此外，我們與衛福部南區緊急災難應變中心合作，期望研發一套災難偵察與追蹤系統，最初我們透過收集與過濾社群媒體中的訊息，幫助值班人員能即時地監控是否有災難事件發生，並追蹤相關訊息；接著我們會將大量訊息進行資料分群，以彙集特定事件的相關訊息並妥善處理雜訊問題，以幫助決策者了解相關災情，做出適當的應對;最終我們會與其他子計畫的成果進行系統整合，形成更全面的災情追蹤與管理平台，且會將災情相關數據融合資料視覺化技術，以方便相關人員進行災後檢討，更提升對於後續災難的防患意識。','Natural and human-made disasters can both cause severe casualties and economic damages. One of the most challenging tasks for agencies in disaster management is to rapidly and accurately identify the latest status of a disaster event. With the recent widespread of social media (e.g., Twitter, Facebook, and PTT,) people may quickly disseminate and share what they see and hear when they witness a severe accident. These massive and instant messages containing texts, photos, and videos may form a new type of channel that usually spreads information faster than traditional media do. In this project, we consider three significant tasks for disaster management, including the response during a disaster, the recovery after a disaster, and the awareness before a disaster. These tasks correspond to the respective goals in each year of this project. Also, we collaborate with the team members of South Regional Emergency Operation Center, Ministry of Health and Welfare in this project. The target is to develop a disaster detection and tracking system. In the beginning, messages from social media are crawled and filtered to help the staff on duty identify if a disaster event happens. Then, similar messages are clustered to show only event-related messages and to reduce noises properly. This approach helps the decision-maker to clarify the whole situation so as have appropriate action. Finally, the proposed systems of corresponding projects are integrated to form a disaster management platform. Data visualization techniques are also utilized to facilitate the review of handling a disaster event. Furthermore, better preparedness for future disasters can thus be achieved.'),(4,107,'2018/06','2019/05','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','運用低功耗廣域物聯網於智慧電網之需求面管理架構','需求面管理、低功耗廣域物聯網、智慧閘道器','Demand-Side Management, Low-Power Wide-Area Network, Smart Gateway','智慧電網是指將供電端到用電端的所有設備，透過感測器連接，形成綿密完整的用電網路，並對其中資訊加以整合分析，以達到電力資源的最佳配置，藉此降低成本、提升可靠性、提高用電效率。有別於傳統人工抄表方式，由於智慧電網中的各項設備均有通訊介面，因此用電戶可即時地獲取用電資訊，而可進一步地配合政府與電力公司所提出的經濟誘因或技術方法，以調整用電尖峰時段的能源需量，來達成需求面管理之目的。 在與台科電公司的前一期計畫「能源視窗之嵌入式系統與雲端應用程式研發 (科技部補助產學合作計畫[開發型]，執行期間：2017/2~2018/1)」中，我們提出了能源視窗的概念並加以實作完成，讓工業、學校、機關團體或中小型企業等用電戶的管理者，能夠透過一個智慧閘道器來彙整其轄下的用電資訊，傳送並保存於一雲端主機。因此，在本計畫中，我們進一步地希望引入低功耗廣域物聯網 (Low-Power Wide-Area Network) 的技術，讓用電環境是位置偏遠、特殊建築或不易佈線施工時，亦能用無線通訊的方式傳送資料。 明確地而言，本計畫所提出之運用低功耗廣域物聯網於智慧電網之需求面管理架構，涵蓋了低功耗廣域網路智慧閘道器及雲端電力需求面管理資料分析，讓人們可透過無線閘道器進行彈性能源管理系統設置，並利用手機或電腦來遠端、即時地監控及管理各項用電資訊並參與需量反應。此一架構由許多不同的軟硬體單元組合而成 ，其中硬體重要組成即是無線智慧閘道器，我們將以NB-IoT及LoRa兩樣技術實作窄頻長距傳輸的低能耗智慧閘道器，軟體重要組成為具提供用戶能源需求面分析的雲端網頁服務管理介面，使智慧閘道器對內能彙整用電資訊、對外與雲端主機雙向溝通，並與雲端系統整合，進而達到能源需求面管理目的。','In smart grids, all energy devices are connected to form a dense network. Through proper techniques of data analytics, usage data can be transformed into invaluable information for the optimized deployment of power resources and better system efficiency. Unlike the traditional manual approach to read electricity meters, users can obtain corresponding usage data instantly through the communication interfaces in smart grids. This helps to achieve the demand-side management. We have developed a smart gateway in our previous project. Also, we propose to incorporate the LPWAN techniques in this project. Specifically, we use NB-IoT and LoRa as hardware components and develop cloud-based user interfaces to realize the purpose of demand-side management.'),(5,106,'2017/02','2018/01','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','能源視窗之嵌入式系統與雲端應用程式研發','智慧電錶、遠端抄表、需量反應','smart meters, remote meter reading, demand response','本計畫所研發之「能源視窗」架構涵蓋了智慧閘道管理及雲端抄表系統，讓人們可利用手機或電腦來遠端、即時地監控及管理各項用電資訊。此一情境的真實體現須由許多不同的軟硬體單元組合而成，其中最關鍵的角色即是智慧閘道器，我們以ARM架構的開發板實作出一嵌入式系統硬體，並結合MQTT通訊協定實現雲端環境中的應用服務，此一閘道器對內能彙整多個電表的用電資訊、對外能與雲端主機雙向溝通，從而實現遠端抄表、用電量分析、需量反應及遠端控制等特色功能。對為數眾多的中小企業而言，未來引入此一架構後，便可往自主智慧節能的目標邁進一大步。','In this project, the proposed \"energy window\" is a novel architecture for electricity consumers to remotely and instantly monitor and manage their usage information. Different hardware and software components should be carefully integrated so as to put this conceptual architecture into practice. Specifically, the smart gateway plays the most critical role in this architecture. To implement this smart gateway, an ARM-based embedded system is developed. Also, the MQTT protocol is used to exchange required messages so as to realize the targeting application service. Note that this smart gateway gathers electricity consumption information from several meters and communicates with a cloud server. Advantageous features of our architecture include remote meter reading, usage analysis, demand response and remote control. For numerous small and medium enterprises in Taiwan, this project delivers valuable results to help them achieve the goal of autonomous energy management.'),(6,102,'2013/08','2014/07','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','結合社群智慧之非同步協作搜尋技術','協作搜尋、社群智慧、使用者體驗、網頁搜尋','collaborative search, collective intelligence, user experience, web search','隨著近年來資通訊科技的快速發展，許多人們的日常生活已 與網路服務有著密不可分的關係，而網頁搜尋更是其中最具 影響力的創新工具，讓人們能隨時隨地獲取所需的資訊；然 而，產學界迄今的研究發展方向仍多僅偏重於個人化搜尋， 可適用於群體 (例如：工作同事、共同修課的小組成員、一 同規劃自助旅行的好友等) 的搜尋模式，卻尚未引起廣大的 研究興趣；因此，我們在本研究計畫中提出在搜尋過程中導 入群體智慧的觀念，當使用者們即使面對不太熟悉的搜尋目 標時，也能有效率地集結眾人的意見進而轉化為決策，更規 劃能讓使用者們以非同步的方式，亦即在不同時間、地點都 可以分工合作，以達到協作搜尋的效果。我們強調透過此系 統，讓使用者可以在非同步的情況下進行協作搜尋，並且解 決了在搜尋過程中需要的使用者互動及任務規劃的問題。最 後，我們提出了數個不同的使用者情境，用以評估及驗證所 提技術對於協作搜尋的可行性及效能。','As information and telecommunication technologies advance at a rapid pace recently, network services have already become an inseparable part of one｀s daily life for many people. Web search is then undoubtedly a major entry of the Internet for most users when acquiring information, especially for mobile users. However, the recent research direction of this field is too much focused on the improvement of personalized search. We thus propose in this work an idea of collaborative search to reflect the collective intelligence of colleagues working on the same project, students taking the same course, friends planning an upcoming trip and so on. With a proper cooperation, users may work together during their search process in an efficient way even if they are not familiar with their search target. Also, it is noted that users may conduct their search activities in different time and places. We emphasize such an asynchronous style of collaborative search and especially address the features of user interaction and task planning in this work. Moreover, several usage scenarios are developed to verify the feasibility of the proposed technique in accomplishing collaborative search.'),(7,100,'2011/08','2012/10','鄧維光','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','建構情報式網頁搜尋之使用者行為模式與探索歷程','瀏覽歷程、人機互動、資訊線索、網頁搜尋','browsing history, human-computer interaction, information cue, web search','現今的網路使用者利用搜尋引擎快速蒐集想要的資訊已經是非常普遍的方式。當在進行情報式網頁搜尋時，目的是要去了解或學習一項知識，如果知識是較為複雜抑或使用者不熟悉之領域，搜尋的過程可能效率不彰。為了幫助使用者有效率地進行情報式網頁搜尋，在觀察使用者進行了解知識的過程中，一個重點是使用者所獲取的資訊線索會不斷累積。現有的搜尋引擎沒有辦法根據使用者累積的資訊立即反應使用者對於資訊的喜好程度，導致使用者必須檢查大量的搜尋結果從中找出當下最合適的網頁。我們因此提出一個指標去反映對搜尋結果使用者當下感興趣的程度。進行情報式網頁搜尋的過程經常使用大量的關鍵字探索不同的主題。然而，使用者對於不同主題感興趣的程度也隨著資訊累積的過程而有改變。具體而言，有關聯的主題之間相同的內容很有可能彼此相互存在，所以當使用者了解了某個主題的部分內容，對於其他關聯的主題也能有一定程度的了解。我們綜合以上的概念，利用使用者探索知識的過程中不斷累積的網頁資訊，從中探索使用者當下的興趣，並且以視覺的形式反映在搜尋結果中。','It is common that users collect desired information by search engines. When an informational web search is performed, users want to understand and learn the particular knowledge. It is difficult to reach the search requirement if the knowledge is unfamiliar to the user or the informational task is complicated. Some efforts are required to browse and to understand the web pages contained in the corresponding search result. In such an informational web search, it is noted that information cues are cumulated as the user reads more and more web pages to approach the search target. In this work, an indicator, i.e., immediacy of interest, is proposed to evaluate the possible user interest toward a web page contained in the search result. Moreover, to address the relevance among search sessions, the topic map is also utilized in our proposed scheme.'),(8,108,'2019/08','2020/07','侯廷偉','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','子計畫:建構緊急災情三維空間資訊蒐集及整合平台(II)',NULL,NULL,'本計畫所開發之母子型災難應變機器人，在災難應變機器人領域應會有學術上創新的機構, 另外,本計畫將機器學習應用到空拍照片及地面照相尋找穿戴衣物，鞋帽以及倖存者有有其重要性，也有機會創新。在移動的物體上辨識音源是最近一兩年受到重視的實務問題，娛樂型或陪伴型機器人也需要，以有機會創新。',NULL),(9,108,'2019/06','2020/05','侯廷偉','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','應用深度學習於人體辨識之節能電網',NULL,NULL,'本計畫之研究改良了傳統節能系統產品與過去相關研究之缺點，能精確得知目標空間中已經無人,依此控制目標空間中之冷氣機，將可比現有解法有更好的節能成效。市場上目前並無此類產品。提出之解法，具備低硬體成本、易建置、高擴充性等特色，並可於適當時機自動關閉電器以減少大量的電力浪費，並可提供多種用電資訊予空間管理者，尤其是公共空間之規劃以及電器的使用得以更有效率，並適合大量裝設於多種公共場所，可為社會帶來大量的節能效益。',NULL),(14,104,'2015/08/','2016/12','侯廷偉','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','應用於婦癌術後預防下肢淋巴水腫之e化運動方案','RGB-D 感測器、Kinect感測器、姿勢比對、復健技術','RGB-D sensor, Kinect sensor, Posture comparison, Rehabilitation technique','本研究針對婦癌的手術治療後術後的運動治療，尤其是下肢淋巴水 腫。 本計畫提出支援婦癌術後病人的e 化運動方案因此包含二大項 目：「動作偵測運動教學系統」，以及評估統計病人運動成效的「 個案運動管理平台」。本計畫透過動作偵測系統建構在醫院中可教 授雙人的運動動作教學系統，主動針對病患運動教學或自我運動治 療的紀錄進行分析，提示個管師自動關懷個案。本計畫中將需解決 主要的問題有： (1) 以家用型的動作偵測系統，正確識別出病患與輔助者的動作姿 勢，並予以提示操作正確與否。 (2) 分析運動資訊，能夠預警出可能未正確達成運動目標之病患。 由於本研究之執行時間原提出為二年，核准縮減至一年，但仍 將「動作偵測運動教學系統」以及「個案運動管理平台」之核心功 能完成。原提出之「運動輔助追蹤系統」之擴增實境功能則留待以 後實現。','The exercises for women after gynecological cancer are important but often not noticed. However, without proper care of the patients, they may have lower limb lymphedema. This research is motivated to build an information system to help the patients learn to have good exercises and especially to prevent lymphedema. The proposed e-exercise system consists of three subsystems: the in-hospital training subsystem, the in-home exercise subsystem, and the case manager’s(nurse’s) subsystem. The major technological issues to be solved are: (1) How to use RGB-D based home devices to detect/distinguish the differences between the trainee’s and the trainer’s postures, and identify how good are the trainee’s postures. (2) To predict or find those patients who may not take exercises accordingly, and report them to the case manager. Due to the reduction of execution period, the core modules of the proposed three subsystems are implemented, except for the augmented reality module of in-home exercise subsystem.'),(15,102,'2013/08','2014/10','侯廷偉','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','容易使用之數位家庭服務組合','Android, OSGi, 智能環境','Android, OSGi, Smart Environment','本計畫提出組合服務的運算子，以運算子結合現有服務，以 形成新的組合服務（情境）的數位家庭環境中的流程控制方 法。實作則以智慧型手持裝置結合 OSGi 系統，建置服務鍵 結、情境建置與服務組合模型等功能。使用者能夠快速得知 裝置的即時狀態，並利用服務組合模型與情境建置功能，簡 單的組合已登錄在 OSGi 中之服務，創造出新的組合服務。 此外本計畫提出裝置自動註冊與裝置狀態隨機切換功能，前 者讓使用者無需專業人員的協助也能夠自行完成裝置的安 裝，後者讓情境能夠跳脫固定模式。','The key idea of this research is to propose a set of operators which could be used to connect existing services to form new composed-services（scenarios） in a smart home environment. The prototype includes an OSGi platform devices and smart handheld devices. Service Binder, Service Composition Model and Scenario Builder are key components of this smart home system. A user could use Service Composition Model and Scenario Builder to easily compose services which are registered in OSGi, and create new services. Besides, this research developed Automatic Registration Device and Random Function. The former reliefs users from service providers＇ help, and the latter provides users a feature to control a device to escape from a fixed behavior.'),(16,101,'2012/08','2013/10','侯廷偉','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','使用者為中心之輕量級智能環境服務組合模型','服務組合, OSGi, 智能環境','Service Composition, OSGi, Smart Environment','本研究著重在如何將周遭的環境與消費性電 子產品結合來組合出更多元及多樣化的服務 (Service Composition)。組合模型通常需要要求使 用者擁有較高的技術門檻，對於使用者來說需要 透過學習和訓練才能使用，造成使用上的不便利 性；另外對於開發者而言則需要學習複雜的數學 和資料模型，進而增加開發的複雜性和維護成 本。本研究針對這兩大缺點建立一個簡單易用的 服務組合模組，利用 OSGi 技術來同時兼顧開發 者與使用者觀點，我們提出一個輕量級智能環境 服務組合模型，並加以實作完成。','This is on existing services researches combining to create diverse and multiple services, which is called Service Composition. However, service composition has two issues. One is that it requires higher entrance barriers which is the holdback toward users. Users need to learn and train in order to use services this model. Another is the complexity and maintaining cost for developers. Our research is to approach those two issues and to build a simple and easy to use service composition model. A light-weight service composition model is proposed and implemented.'),(17,100,'2011/08','2012/07','侯廷偉','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','OSGi服務平台之自動化資源管理架構','自動化資源管理, OSGi, 相依性分析, Java 虛擬機器','Automatic resource management, OSGi, Dependency analysis, Java virtual machine','Open Services Gateway Initiative (OSGi) 近年來憑藉其 高度動態適應性、模組化以及基於 Java 技術等特性，持續活 耀於居家照護、保全系統、家庭娛樂等領域。隨著 OSGi 服務 平台所執行的應用程式數量及複雜度不斷增加，加上消費性 電子的資源有限(特別是計算能力和記憶體資源)，導致系統 上資源分配與管理的工作愈形沉重，逐漸突顯出 OSGi 規格對 於資源管理上的不足。有鑑於此，本研究提出一個 OSGi 服務 平台資源管理架構，並透過基於此架構的雛型進行一系列模 擬實驗。結果顯示，此架構可有效解決 Service 資源配置與 釋放的問題，除提昇平台的資源可利用性，並可降低應用程 式開發者手動管理資源配置與釋放的困難度。','In recent years, Open Services Gateway Initiative (OSGi) has been successfully applied to many fields, including home healthcare, security system, home entertainments, etc. More and more embedded devices have selected OSGi as the software management platform. As a result, numerous complex services/applications have emerged and are installed/ run on the OSGi platform, thus increasing the overhead of the resource management on the OSGi platform. Since most of the embedded devices are typically resource-constrained, the resource management on OSGi becomes a key issue and this is the main subject of this project. In this project, we propose an automatic resource management architecture for the OSGi service platform, which is based on investigating how to enhance the efficiency of resource utilization in terms of the service activation and deactivation. By exploiting the runtime services dependencies and part of the resource access patterns defined in the OSGi framework, the existing OSGi resource management method can be further improved. In addition, our simulation results show that the proposed approach performs well for a wide range of bundles/applications, and the processing overhead is quite low.'),(18,106,'2017/08','2019/01','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','子計畫五：以設計思考融入程式設計課程','關鍵詞：設計思考、STEAM創客、跨領域教育、程式設計','_Design Thinking, STEAM Maker, Interdisciplinary Learning, Programming Design_','本計畫主要目的在針對大專院校學生，設計及發展一套能輔助設計思考養成與STEAM創客元素融入程式設計的課程研發，本計畫之課程設計構想乃是依據總計畫所提出之STEAM創客的課程評建規範，並配合子計畫一所開發的數位學習共享平台。為此本計畫所發展之課程設計將導入設計思考框架、STEAM知識整合框架兩大要素於跨領域的程式設計課程開發，研究將分成三個階段，預計以三年的時間完成。第一年的研究重點在於設計思考、STEAM框架的分析、整合與初步建構課程雛型；第二年著重於將課程雛型施行於實際教學場域進行前導研究，其中必須觀察學生的學習歷程、行為以及回饋。另外，也必須一併考量相關專家的意見以及總計畫之評鑑規範，以供本計畫進行後續的教學與課程調整。第三年則以前兩年所得之研究成果進行本計畫研發之課程的實踐，以落實總計畫的STEAM創客以及跨領域之理念，也幫助學生學習到設計思考的方法，使學生除了STEAM知識與技術的學習之外，在未來也具有能力開創有價值的前瞻應用。本計畫預計以分段實驗方式進行檢核與評估，來瞭解並驗證所設計之課程的可行性與實用性。預期本研究之成果將可作為探究學生知識學習以及創造力發展之狀況，以作為後續調整STEAM以及創造力發展等相關領域的參考。','	The main purpose of this project is to design and develop a curriculum structure for program design that helps promoting design thinking and realizes the STEAM Maker elements. The design of the curriculum structure follows the evaluation rules developed by the main project and is to use the e-learning platform developed by subproject 1 for teaching practices. The curriculum structure uses a design thinking framework to enhance students’ creative thinking and a STEAM Maker knowledge framework to immerse students in hands-on experiences on designing creative and robust software. The project consists of three major phases, to be finished in three years. Works for the first phases focus on the analysis and designing of both the design thinking and the STEAM Maker knowledge frameworks and on embedding them into a prototype structure of the curriculum. A pilot teaching experiment on the curriculum kicks off the work of the second phase to produce students’ learning profiles, behavior, and feedbacks, on which invited experts examine and analyze, following the evaluation rules from the main project, to give suggestions for adjustments and modifications on the structure of the curriculum and the teaching activities. In the third phase, the project starts to conduct a full scale teaching experiments on the curriculum, aiming to fulfill the multi-disciplines STEAM Maker ideas to help students mastering the technique of design thinking and make them using STEAM Maker knowledge and skills to create valuable innovative robust software. Two successive experiments in the second and third phases will be able to check、evaluate、and prove the feasibility and practicability of the designed structure of the curriculum. The result of this project can also produce portfolios of STEAM Maker knowledge learning profiles and creative thinking developing processes that serve as references for developments of curriculum of various courses on STEAM Maker concepts.'),(19,105,'2016/08','2017/10','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','開放式問答自我解釋字串之語意分析及應用-以一客製化C++程式撰寫系統為例','開放式問答、自我解釋策略、自然語言處理、C++程式概念迷思','open question, self-explanation learning strategy, natural language processing, C++ programming misconceptions.','	自我解釋(Self-explanation)意指學習者針對問題解決或是某事物本身所作的相關推論或解釋，以建立相關的領域概念。已有許多研究證明自我解釋策略可以有效幫助學習者釐清概念、整合新舊知識。而若搭配問答的方式引導學習者進行自我解釋，則更可以提升自我解釋之成效。然而也有進一步研究指出，學生在進行自我解釋的過程中可能會產生錯誤的解釋，致使學習者因此建構錯誤的概念。因此施教者應適時給予相關的教學回饋，及時來導正學習者之概念。而C++程式語言為大學工程類科系的熱門必修學科，其複雜之概念經常讓學習者在學習的過程中產生概念的混淆及迷思，進而阻礙其學習。 為提升自我解釋及教學回饋之成效，本研究選用開放式問答的自我解釋學習策略，學習者進行自我解釋時以自然語言輸入他們的想法與推論，系統再使用自然語言處理(NLP)技術針對學習者所輸入之自我解釋字串進行語意分析，藉此分析學習者對於該解釋處之概念理解程度及是否存在概念迷思(Misconceptions)，並適時給予相關引導教材作為回饋，盼能即時導正學習者的領域概念。為了瞭解本研究方法的可行性，本研究以C++程式設計領域為例，開發一具有自我解釋學習策略之C++線上程式撰寫系統。實驗設計上，本研究徵求30位修習過C++程式設計課程的大學部學生使用本研究所開發之系統進行實際的程式上機練習，並蒐集學習者所有的程式編寫歷程，藉此計算本系統學習者自我解釋字串語意分析之準確率。實驗結果發現本研究所開發之系統針對學習者自我解釋正確與否的判斷準確率達91.8%，而C++程式概念迷思教材的推薦準確率達88.1%。','Self-explanation gives an explicit expression on what is your thought or inference on the domain concepts of an entity generated by an activity you are engaging in. Many researches have proven that self-explanation strategy is an effective learning strategy that can help learners clarify their concepts and merge them with their knowledge. Moreover, an open-question based self-explanation strategy, which asks learners to give their self-explanation sentences to the questions, is more efficient for learning. However, studies have pointed out shortcomings of open question based self-explanation strategy, i.e. without proper prior knowledge, a user’s self-explanation may generate errors and result in constructing error concepts if proper guidance were not given. Error concepts surely will become obstacles in further knowledge constructions. It is important to give teaching material feedbacks to learners if their self-explanations have misconceptions. On the other hand, C++ programming language is the must course for most engineering students. However, its complicated programming concepts usually make student lost and confused. This study uses C++ programming language as the subject and constructs an online programming system embedded with self-explanation strategy that gives users instant feedbacks to correct their possible misconceptions. The self-explanation strategy uses open questions, so that it can ask programmer to give their self-explanations on their thoughts and inferences by their nature language. The system uses natural language processing technology for semantic analysis on self-explanation sentences and, according to the result, gives proper feedbacks to learners to revise their misconceptions. The final evaluation experiment recruited 30 college students who used this system for actual C++ programming. The system records all students’ programming activities, analyzes their self-explanations for misconceptions, and gives proper feedbacks for students. Verified manually by programming experts, the system reaches an average of 91.8% accuracy of misconception identification in self-explanation sentence processing and reaches an average of 88.1% accuracy in teaching material recommendation for the misconceptions.'),(21,104,'2015/08','2016/12','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','工程教育扎根計畫─融入國小自然、數學、與生活科技課程之STEM導向工程教育課程設計暨數位學習平台的建置','準工程教育、STEM專題式學習、數位學習平台','Pre-engineering Education, STEM-oriented Project-based',' 現今的畢業的小學生在十年後將逐漸對台灣工程科技發展產生長遠','In a decade, students graduate today from primary schools'),(23,103,'2014/08','2015/12','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','結合自我解釋策略於國小學童互動虛擬實驗室環境的建置與實證','自我解釋、虛擬實驗室、科學實驗',' Self-explanation, Virtual Laboratory, Science Experiment','本研究目的在於設計與實作一個以自我解釋策略為基礎並適用於國','This project aims to design and implement an interactive'),(24,102,'2012/08','2014/10','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','整合變易理論之物件導向程式設計適性化網路學習環境的建置與應用研究','變易理論、物件導向程式設計、智慧型教學代理人、網路學','variation theory, intelligent teaching agents,','本計畫導入變易理論（variation theory）教學模式以發展','The purpose of this project is to design and'),(25,101,'2010/08','2013/07','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','具三段式對話模式之智慧型英語文法數位學習系統的建置與評估','IRF 教學對話、發問與回饋、英語文法學習、英語輔助學習','IRF Dialogue, Questioning and Feedback, English','本研究的主要目的是結合 IRF 教學對話模式，設計並開發一','This project integrates the Initiation, Response, and'),(27,100,'2009/08','2012/07','王宗一','國立成功大學工程科學系（所）','結合知識地圖以呈現學習概念能量之國小線上試題評量系統的設計、建置與實證','智慧型網路評量系統、知識地圖、Bloom 教育目標分類、試','knowledge map, domain concept, energy appraisal,','本研究主要目的針對國小教師發展及設計一套能輔助出題的','The purpose of this project is to design and'),(28,106,'2017/08','2018/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','使用遞迴最近點演算法及主動式視覺實現在無顯著特徵環境下之機器人定位','最近遞迴點，機器人感知，多機器人合作','Iterative closest point, robot perception, multi-robot collaboration','國際世界盃機器人足球競賽標準平台聯盟所使用的足球場場地在過去幾年間有過幾次重大的改變。現今標準平台聯盟技術委員會所採用的場地已經成為一個完全對稱而且缺乏像球門柱一樣顯著特徵的環境。過往所使用的黃色球門柱很容易在遠處被偵測到，任何一種定位演算法皆能因看見黃色球門柱而維持良好的定位結果。但若要開發一個偵測白色球門柱的演算法而且效能如同過往同偵測黃色球門柱一般，機器人將花費更多的資源在執行這項運算。由於聯盟所採用的機器人有運算效能的限制，多數的參賽隊伍也不願意開發昂貴的演算法用來偵測除了較原始的角落特徵或點特徵。無顯著特徵的環境也限縮了我們所使用的多機器人同時定位並追蹤演算法的表現。 　我們了解到即使機器人在有些開闊的場地上只能看見稀疏的角落特徵或點特徵，場地線卻是隨處可見。在這項計畫書中我們開發能與原來的多機器人同時定位並追蹤演算法相容的架構，使用場地線作為特徵的定位演算法。藉由使用遞迴最近點演算法，我們能將量測到的場地線特徵和其他較原始的特徵如角落特徵與已知的足球場地地圖貼合。我們將使用機器人里程計獲得對自身座標的預測作為遞迴最近點演算法的初始猜測，其貼合結果將會得到一個新的機器人位置估測。此估測將成為一個結合多項原始特徵的新特徵用於更新擴展卡曼濾波器狀態估測。 　除了使用場地線以增進定位的結果，我們同時希望機器人能增加從每張影像上獲取重要特徵的可能性。考慮機器人會同時需要執行自我定位、追蹤球、避開障礙物和許多其他工作，每項工作卻都可能需要來自機器人不同方位的特徵量測。然而機器人的馬達本身是有限制的。為了使機器人能更有效率處理各項工作，我們在此計畫中開發能夠安排機器人頭部轉動之先後順序，以最大化獲取所有工作執行所需要的資訊。','The settings of RoboCup SPL soccer field has been experienced several significant changes during the past three years. The soccer field that the official SPL technical committee adopted now is completely symmetric and lack of distinctive primitive features such as yellow goalposts. The yellow goalpost used in the past was easy to be detected from distances and it favors any localization algorithm. With the white goalpost nowadays, to come up with a new algorithm to perform as good as yellow goalpost detectors will cost too much overhead. Due to the hardware limitation on the used robot, many teams would choose not to develop expensive algorithms to detect features besides some primitive corners or points. In our own system, the lack of distinctive features also cause our MR-SLAT algorithm loses its performance. 　Our observations show that even though primitive corners or points are sparse for robots to see at some open space on the field, field lines are still observable almost everywhere. In this proposal we propose a method to make use of the field line features and incorporate with the original MR-SLAT algorithm. With the use of iterative closest point (ICP) algorithm, we can fit the field line measurements as well as other primitive features such as corners to our known soccer map. The initial guess of ICP will use predicted robot pose from odometer. The result will provide an estimated robot pose. Such estimated robot pose will be used as a combinative measurement as it has already been included with many of other measurements and will be used to update EKF state estimator. 　Besides the use of line features to improve the localization result, we also aim at gaining the significant measurement acquired from each image. And also considering a robot may concurrently doing self- localization, ball tracking, obstacle avoidance, and many of the other things, each of them require different measurements coming from different orientations to the robot. But the robot itself has constraints regarding the joint limitations. To make the robot handle each task efficiently, the system schedules the sequence of head actions to maximize the required information for each task.'),(29,105,'2016/08','2017/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','用於多機器人合作之基於效用性質的時效性資訊傳輸架構','關鍵幀選取，合作系統，多機器人合作，效用性函數','	Keyframe selection, cooperative systems, multi-robot collaboration, utility function','	多機器人合作可改善個別機器人有限的感測、認知與計算能力，整合個別機器人所感測到 的資訊、認知的結果與計算能力，共同完成單一機器人無法完成的任務。多機器人協同 定位與追蹤（Multi-robot Simultaneous Localization and Tracking, MR-SLAT）理論能在 完美的通訊條件下提供良好的定位結果。但該理論在量測更新（Measurement Update）步 驟中，隨著機器人之間分享的量測（Measurement）的數量增加，會對系統產生顯著的負 擔。實務層面上由於機器人通常不具有高階運算處理單元，以及無線通訊多半無法維持理 想穩定的條件，減少冗餘量測是一項提升多機器人合作定位演算法計算速度的策略。本研 究基於多機器人協同定位與追蹤得理論架構，於前處理部分提出一關鍵幀選取（Keyframe Selection）架構以減少冗餘的特徵量測。我們基於資訊熵（Shannon Entropy）理論並提出 評估量測的效用性函數計算方式，對個別機器人從影像上所擷取較底層的動態與靜態物 體資料分別進行效用性評估。若該影像中的效用性夠大，亦即該影像含有夠多的資訊變 化，此影像即可視為一關鍵幀。此關鍵幀將被用於與後來之影像比較資訊變化量，並且進 一步被機器人用以擷取各項特徵之量測，以及用於多機器人合作感知與定位（Multi-robot Cooperative Perception and Localizaiton）。實驗結果顯示適當的關鍵幀選取參數即使在 不使用從所有影像擷取出的量測進行量測更新步驟，多機器人合作定位的結果依然能有合 理的準確度。','Multiple-robot cooperation can lift the limitation on sensing, perception, and computation capability of single robot to accomplish the task that cannot be accomplished by single robot. Multi-robot cooperative localization and tracking, or MR-SLAT, can provide good localiza- tion result under stable communication situation. But considering the step of measurement update in the algorithm, the amount of measurements sharing among robots will cause sig- nicant burden to the system. In practical applications, robots usually don\'t have sucient computation units and the quality of communication might not be stable all the time. Hence reducing redundant measurements is a strategy for the system to reduce the time spent on computing localization algorithm. This work is based on the framework of MR-SLAT and propose a keyframe selection mechanism as a preprocessing for MR-SLAT. The purpose is to select proper keyframes to reduce the redundant measurements. We incorporate Shan- non Entropy theory and provide a mechanism for calculating the utility of measurements. For each low-level data extracted from an image depending on whether its from a moving object or a stationary object, we calculate its utility. If the data extracted from an image has high utility, meaning the image has signicant information change compared with the previous keyframe, the image will be selected as the next keyframe and the data extracted from the image will be used for object detection modules as well as for measurement update of multi-robot cooperative perception and localization. The experimental results show that with proper keyframe selection parameters the results of multi-robot cooperative perception can have feasible accuracy using small fraction of image data.'),(30,104,'2015/08','2016/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','關鍵性任務物聯網系統之資料品質保證架構','物聯網，中介軟體，資料品質保證','Internet-of-Things, Middleware, Quality of Data Guarantee','智慧整合控制系統(Cyber-Physical Systems)與物聯網(Internetof-Things)應',' IoT and CPS technologies can be applied to many application'),(31,103,'2014/08','2015/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','以互動式示範學習完成動態環境中多機器人之導航與合作','機器人導航，自示範中學習，模仿學習，多機器人合作感知，適應',' Robot Navigation, Learning from Demonstration, Imitation','近年來 本團隊著力在多機器人感知理論 與演算法的研發，並將所','Theory and algorithms of multi-robot perception have been'),(32,103,'2014/08','2015/10','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','適用於智慧整合控制系統之彈性計算架構','智慧整合控制系統，非精確計算',' Cyber-Physical Systems, Imprecise Computation','現今在行動運算上的運用越來越多樣化，許許多多的行動運用藉著',' The contribution of this work is to enable time-sensitive,'),(33,102,'2013/05','2014/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','異質通訊網路之即時防災救災訊息中介軟體','異質通訊網路, 中介軟體，防災，救災 ','Heterogeneous Network, Middleware, Disaster','自然與人為的災害會造成在網絡硬體的損壞並導致通信服務',NULL),(34,101,'2012/01','2013/03','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','Android平台最佳化技術研究之建置計畫(III)','省電, 虛擬平台, 虛擬化, 多媒體, 雲端服務 ','energy-saving, virtual platform, virtualization,','本計畫開發 Android 行動平台上的最佳化技術，建置在市售','This project develops optimization technologies for'),(35,101,'2010/08','2013/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','流程導向之實體數位系統架構與開發環境研究','智慧整合控制系統 中介軟體 分散式系統 使用者需求分析','Cyber-Physical Systems, Middleware, Distributed','此項計畫研究與設計一個開放式嵌入式軟體系統架構，以提','The research focus of this project is on a framework'),(36,100,'2011/05','2012/07','施吉昇','國立臺灣大學資訊網路與多媒體研究所','子計畫三：支援OpenCL之虛擬雲端多核心行動平台架構之研究(I)','開放計算語言、雲端運算、通用圖形處理器、工作負載轉','OpenCL, Cloud computing, GPGPU, Workload migration,','現今行動運算平台如手機，筆記型電腦，與平板電腦，已逐','People use mobile devices to perform more and more');
